<plot>Mr. Calverone is diagnosed with terminal lung cancer and only given a month or two to live. While leaving his doctor's office, he is enticed by Louie to play a simple card game. The game allows Mr. Calverone to make a wish; his wish is to live. And that's just what happens, he lives; with terminal cancer!</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?601505</url></doc>
